{"word":"αἰγίς","slug":"αἰγίς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n2177\" key=\"ai)gi/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">αἰγίς</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ίδος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, (<itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">αῐξ</itype>, cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νεβρίς</foreign>): <sense n=\"I\" id=\"n2177.0\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">goatskin</tr_>, worn as a dress, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:189\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.189</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg001.perseus-grc1:360\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cyc.\">Cyc.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">360</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.); hence, </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n2177.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> esp. the skin shield of Zeus, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:738\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.738</biblScope></bibl>, al.; lent by him to Athena, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:447\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.447</biblScope></bibl>, al.; to Apollo, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:15:318\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.318</biblScope></bibl>, al.; later, with fringe of snakes and <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gorgon\">Gorgon</a></author> </bibl>'s head, the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">aegis</tr_> of Athena, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg007.perseus-grc1:404\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eu.\">Eu.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">404</biblScope></bibl>, etc. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n2177.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> dress worn by priestess of Athena, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0034.tlg002:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Lycurg.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n2177.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> ornamentworn on the breast, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:5:100\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.100</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"5\" id=\"n2177.4\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cuirass</tr_> (<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lacon.\">Lacon.</a></gram> </gramGrp>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0578.tlg001:22\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Nymphod.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n2177.5\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">rushing storm, hurricane</tr_>, terrible as the shaken aegis, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg006.perseus-grc1:593\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ch.\">Ch.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">593</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0486.tlg001:117\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Pherecr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">117</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aristid.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.487</biblScope> </bibl> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ J.\">J.</a></author></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2200.tlg004:18:268\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lib.\">Lib.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Or.\">Or.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.268</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n2177.6\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">heart-wood</tr_> of the Corsican pine, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg001:3:9:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thphr.\">Thphr.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HP\">HP</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.9.3</biblScope> </bibl>; in Arcadia also that of the silver-fir, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg001:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8</biblScope> </bibl>; cf. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Ἐφ. Ἀρχ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg001:1895:59\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1895.59</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (<placeName TEIform=\"placeName\">Eleusis</placeName>). </sense> <sense n=\"IV\" id=\"n2177.7\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">speck in the eye</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg017:214\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Coac.\">Coac.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">214</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg016:2:20\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Prorrh.\">Prorrh.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.20</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}